Here You can have Multiple Services having their Own Servers or Containers
Each Service communicates with Other Services via network
Each Service will typically have their own DB.


Pros:
1. Easy to Develop, Test and Deploy.
2. Easily Adapt Changes
3. No Need to deploy Dependent Service or whole Application
4. Parallel Development
5. Services Can choose their Own Database
6. Services can be built with the Help of Other Programming languages even


Cons:
1. Complexity
2. Infrastructure Overhead




